      "updated_at": "2016-04-18 14:35:32 UTC",
      "body": "This is one thing where I believe the formatter should try and preserve whatever was there before. I usually use the separate line variant, except if the filter is \"tightly coupled\" to a `<-` in terms of semantics (which is something the formatter cannot guess).\r\n\r\nIf I were to choose one thing to always conform to, it would be the separate line variant."
    }
