  "closed_at": "2016-05-13 08:20:10 UTC",
  "body": "Diff:\r\n```scala\r\n       for {\r\n          parent <- sym.info.parents\r\n -        psym = parent.typeSymbol\r\n -        if psym.isInterface\r\n +        psym = parent.typeSymbol if psym.isInterface\r\n        } yield {\r\n          genClassName(psym)\r\n        }\r\n```\r\n\r\nI'd like to keep the if where it was. \r\n\r\nUsing: 0.2.1\r\n"
